psalm.text:
[[Ps 5,5]]For you, O God, delight not in wickedness; 
No evil man remains with you;
[[Ps 5,6]]The arrogant may not stand in your sight. 
You hate all evildoers.

[[Ps 5,7]]You destroy all who speak falsehood; 
the bloodthirsty and the deceitful 
the LORD abhors.
[[Ps 5,8]]But I can enter your house because of your great love. 

I can worship in your holy temple 
because of my reverence for you, LORD.
